'''Jacen''' was a stuffed [[Tauntaun/Legends|tauntaun]] that [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] gave to his daughter, [[Allana Djo Solo|Allana]], on a visit to [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]]. Allana named it Jacen so that she could talk to it when Solo did not visit.

